videos.description: Quarterback McKenzie Milton tucks it and runs in for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: UCF's  Milton runs in for TD

videos.description: Frank Nutile lobs it to Keith Kirkwood for a 8-yard touchdown to regain the lead.
videos.headline: Temple's Nutile connects with Kirkwood for TD

videos.description: McKenzie Milton connects with Tre'Quan Smith for a 41-yard gain.
videos.headline: UCF's  Milton throws deep to Smith

videos.description: Tre'Quan Smith shows his concentration by keeping one foot in for the one-handed catch.
videos.headline: UCF's  Smith comes down with the impressive one-handed grab

videos.description: Dredrick Snelson runs in for a 2-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: UCF's Snelson finishes off drive with TD

videos.description: McKenzie Milton finds Otis Anderson for the 9-yard touchdown to extend the Golden Knights' lead.
videos.headline: UCF's Milton dumps it off to Anderson for TD

videos.description: Kyle Gibson makes the  interception and takes it near the goal line to set up good field position for UCF.
videos.headline: UCF's Gibson leaps for interception

videos.description: Otis Anderson avoids defenders for a 32-yard gain putting the Golden Knights near the goal line.
videos.headline: UCF's Anderson gets loose for 32 yards

videos.description: McKenzie Milton finds Tre'Quan Smith  who brakes a tackle for the 22-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: UCF's Smith shakes off defender for TD

videos.description: Shaquem Griffin, who's missing a hand, makes the interception and celebrates with his teammates.
videos.headline: UCF's Griffin continues impressive season with interception

videos.description: Marlon Williams dives and hits the pylon for the 8-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: UCF's Williams dives in for TD

videos.description: Frank Nutile throws a deep strike to Adonis Jennings for a 74-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Temple's Nutile heaves it to Jennings for deep TD
